00:00:53,187 --> 00:00:55,120
            narrator:           
    in the late 19th century,   

11
00:00:55,122 --> 00:00:57,857
    it was considered immoral   
       for unmarried women      

12
00:00:57,859 --> 00:00:59,926
    to enter a man's bedroom.   

13
00:00:59,928 --> 00:01:02,127
     william murphy couldn't    
       bring his date back      

14
00:01:02,129 --> 00:01:03,596
   to his one-room apartment,   

15
00:01:03,598 --> 00:01:06,865
      so he invented a bed      
  that folded up into the wall, 

16
00:01:06,867 --> 00:01:09,068
     converting his bedroom     
          into a parlor         

17
00:01:09,070 --> 00:01:11,070
   to host his love interest.   

18
00:01:14,475 --> 00:01:16,208
 a wall of cupboards and closets

19
00:01:16,210 --> 00:01:17,909
   suddenly opens up to reveal  

20
00:01:17,911 --> 00:01:21,480
        sleek comfortable       
       sleeping quarters.       

21
00:01:21,482 --> 00:01:25,217
   the wall bed is a great way  
      to economize on space     

22
00:01:25,219 --> 00:01:29,021
       without sacrificing      
        comfort or style.       

23
00:01:29,023 --> 00:01:31,090
 to build the mechanism casing, 

24
00:01:31,092 --> 00:01:33,759
       a worker begins by       
     placing the steel plate    

25
00:01:33,761 --> 00:01:35,694
 in a powerful bending machine, 

26
00:01:35,696 --> 00:01:39,465
       which is capable of      
   exerting 55 tons of force.   

27
00:01:42,303 --> 00:01:44,370
 using the square and calipers, 

28
00:01:44,372 --> 00:01:46,772
       the worker verifies      
          that the bend         

29
00:01:46,774 --> 00:01:49,375
     is a perfectly uniform     
           right angle          

30
00:01:49,377 --> 00:01:51,510
      and the flange depth      
         does not exceed        

31
00:01:51,512 --> 00:01:55,114
    the specified parameters.   

32
00:01:55,116 --> 00:01:57,116
    once the bending machine    
           has folded           

33
00:01:57,118 --> 00:01:59,118
  all four sides of the plate,  

34
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:01,787
    the worker then mounts it   
       onto a locator pin       

35
00:02:01,789 --> 00:02:03,122
       in a second press,       

36
00:02:03,124 --> 00:02:05,590
         which descends         
 and creates a small depression 

37
00:02:05,592 --> 00:02:07,360
   around the central opening.  

38
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:16,002
 this depression will facilitate
      the welding process.      

39
00:02:16,004 --> 00:02:17,870
   using another locator pin,   

40
00:02:17,872 --> 00:02:23,142
    a welder clamps the plate   
    into a purpose-built jig.   

41
00:02:23,144 --> 00:02:26,012
   he then begins welding all   
   of the necessary components  

42
00:02:26,014 --> 00:02:28,213
            in place.           

43
00:02:28,215 --> 00:02:30,549
         he uses a bolt         
       to correctly locate      

44
00:02:30,551 --> 00:02:33,885
 an internal reinforcement plate

45
00:02:33,887 --> 00:02:36,688
        and also welds in       
      the crucial pivot pin     

46
00:02:36,690 --> 00:02:38,958
     on which the mechanism     
           will hinge.          

47
00:02:42,096 --> 00:02:44,296
        the casing plates       
     are mounted on spacers     

48
00:02:44,298 --> 00:02:46,698
          to help speed         
       the drying process.      

49
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:50,702
   then a worker spray-paints   
           them black.          

50
00:02:50,704 --> 00:02:55,374
      once dry, he removes      
a protective cap from the pivot.

51
00:02:55,376 --> 00:02:58,044
  it's now time to manufacture  

52
00:02:58,046 --> 00:03:01,246
        the wall-mounted        
        spring mechanism.       

53
00:03:01,248 --> 00:03:04,983
   a worker uses a drill press  
  outfitted with a countersink  

54
00:03:04,985 --> 00:03:10,322
   to create a beveled recess   
      around the openings.      

55
00:03:10,324 --> 00:03:13,325
       a worker then uses       
   a specially-designed press   

56
00:03:13,327 --> 00:03:17,730
   to install a brass bearing   
     in one of the openings.    

57
00:03:17,732 --> 00:03:19,932
          the mechanism         
       is nearly complete.      

58
00:03:21,936 --> 00:03:27,273
however, there are still several
   steps to go in the process.  

59
00:03:27,275 --> 00:03:29,542
  next, a worker brushes grease 

60
00:03:29,544 --> 00:03:33,145
        onto the interior       
    of two mechanism casings.   

61
00:03:33,147 --> 00:03:35,748
     he then flips them over    
        in order to apply       

62
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:38,918
     a specially-formulated     
    grease to the pivot pin.    

63
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:44,022
  he slides the bushing over it 

64
00:03:44,024 --> 00:03:46,992
     and applies a c-shaped     
         locking washer.        

65
00:03:49,396 --> 00:03:52,364
   an s-shaped stop will lock   
     the mechanism in place     

66
00:03:52,366 --> 00:03:54,333
   until the bed is installed.  

67
00:03:56,503 --> 00:03:59,905
 the spring-unit assemblage will
 provide the resistance required

68
00:03:59,907 --> 00:04:02,708
     to help smoothly raise     
       and lower the bed.       

69
00:04:04,912 --> 00:04:10,515
  a locking pin secures one end 
  of the spring unit in place.  

70
00:04:10,517 --> 00:04:12,785
   the worker adds the bottom   
       plate of the unit,       

71
00:04:12,787 --> 00:04:16,522
 which includes a threaded bolt.

72
00:04:16,524 --> 00:04:19,458
     a nut threaded onto it     
  can be tightened or loosened  

73
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:23,195
            to adjust           
    the mechanism's tension.    

74
00:04:23,197 --> 00:04:24,930
        the wall-mounted        
        spring mechanism        

75
00:04:24,932 --> 00:04:28,134
    is ready to be installed.   

76
00:04:28,136 --> 00:04:33,338
    it's designed to connect    
 to this bed-mounted component. 

77
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:34,874
    once mounted to the bed,    

78
00:04:34,876 --> 00:04:37,142
       the two components       
         work together,         

79
00:04:37,144 --> 00:04:40,646
   allowing the user to easily  
    raise and lower the bed.    

80
00:04:43,351 --> 00:04:46,619
    a worker quickly installs   
    the bed-mounted component   

81
00:04:46,621 --> 00:04:50,990
    using pre-drilled holes,    
    bolts, and locking nuts.    

82
00:04:53,427 --> 00:04:56,495
 he installs the wall bed's legs
        in the same way,        

83
00:04:56,497 --> 00:04:58,564
     following a pre-drilled    
          hole pattern          

84
00:04:58,566 --> 00:05:00,299
     to locate the component    

85
00:05:00,301 --> 00:05:01,967
    and attach it with bolts,   

86
00:05:01,969 --> 00:05:05,237
    locking nuts, and screws.   

87
00:05:05,239 --> 00:05:08,374
     the legs fold down when    
      the bed is being used     

88
00:05:08,376 --> 00:05:10,943
     and tuck out of the way    
     when the bed folds up.     

89
00:05:15,383 --> 00:05:17,316
        the manufacturers       
         can now package        

90
00:05:17,318 --> 00:05:20,252
  the fully-assembled wall beds 
          for transport         

91
00:05:20,254 --> 00:05:21,921
     to their destinations.     

92
00:05:24,258 --> 00:05:27,593
     installing the wall bed    
      requires some muscle,     

93
00:05:27,595 --> 00:05:29,995
   but once the two components  
     of the spring mechanism    

94
00:05:29,997 --> 00:05:31,263
         are connected,         

95
00:05:31,265 --> 00:05:33,666
        lowering the bed        
     onto its fold-away legs    

96
00:05:33,668 --> 00:05:35,534
       is a piece of cake.      

97
00:05:38,539 --> 00:05:41,607
       this s-shaped stop       
      ensures the mechanism     

98
00:05:41,609 --> 00:05:43,809
   won't accidentally flip up.  

99
00:05:43,811 --> 00:05:45,277
       once it's removed,       

100
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:48,213
      the bed easily rises.     

101
00:05:48,215 --> 00:05:50,149
  the legs tuck into position,  

102
00:05:50,151 --> 00:05:52,217
  and the bed neatly folds away 

103
00:05:52,219 --> 00:05:53,752
      into its hiding spot,     

104
00:05:53,754 --> 00:05:56,021
 as though it were never there. 

